The recommended dosage of ZYFLO for the symptomatic treatment of patien ts with asthma is one 600-mg tablet four times a day for a total daily dose of 2400 mg. For ease of administration, ZYFLO may be taken with meals and at bedtime. Hepatic transaminases should be evaluated prior to initiation of ZYFLO and periodically during treatment (see PRECAUTIONS, Hepatic). 
